urysm of the Sinus of Valsalva in a Young Woman: A Management Dilemma</a></div><div class="related__authors"><ul class="rlist--inline loa mobile-authors loa-height"><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Marc T Zughaib</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Keyur Patel</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Andrew D Assaf</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Marcel E Zughaib</span></li></ul></div><div class="meta">2026Jan24 | Cureus, Vol. 38</div></div><div class="getFTR external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.7759/cureus.102199">Crossref</a></div></div></li><li class="citedByEntry" data-doi="10.1007/978-981-96-7667-5_10"><div class="related"><div class="related__title"><a target="_blank" href="https://doi.org/10.1007/978-981-96-7667-5_10">Congenital Heart Disease</a></div><div class="related__authors"><ul class="rlist--inline loa mobile-authors loa-height"><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Tiong Cheng Yeo</span></li></ul></div><div class="meta">16 April 2026</div></div><div class="getFTR external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1007/978-981-96-7667-5_10">Crossref</a></div></div></li><li class="citedByEntry" data-doi="10.4330/wjc.v17.i6.102722"><div class="related"><div class="related__title"><a target="_blank" href="https://doi.org/10.4330/wjc.v17.i6.102722">Diagnosis and treatment options for sinus of Valsalva aneurysms: A narrative review</a></div><div class="related__authors"><ul class="rlist--inline loa mobile-authors loa-height"><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Kevan English</span></li></ul></div><div class="meta">26 June 2025 | World Journal of Cardiology, Vol. 17, No. 6</div></div><div class="getFTR external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.4330/wjc.v17.i6.102722">Crossref</a></div></div></li><li class="citedByEntry" data-doi="10.1093/ehjcr/ytaf201"><div class="related